LAND OWNERS ASSOCIATION et al. v. GRAND RAPIDS TRUST COMPANY et al. No. 8370. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. Jan. 18, 1940. Charles S. Abbott, of Ann Arbor, Mich., for appellants. Norris, McPherson, Harrington & Waer and Travis, Merrick' & Johnson, all of Grand Rapids, Mich., for appellees.

Before HICKS and SIMONS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

It is ordered that the appeal herein be and the same is dismissed, pursuant to stipulation of counsel.
